Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph <archive-uri> status

Purpose:
  Show archive readiness and high-level counts.

Usage:
  wikigraph <archive-uri> status [--json]

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: yes.

Examples:
  wikigraph wkg://book.sdpub status
  wikigraph wkg:///Users/me/book.sdpub status --json
